#. ~ Description for UnderrailMetro Mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a variety of items, enemies and locations inspired by the games Metro "
"series and Underrail."
msgstr "添加了多种受《地铁》系列和《Underrail》游戏启发的物品、敌人与地点。"

