#. ~ Profession (male South Gate Civilian) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Seeking refuge away from the maelstrom of pain that is the New England "
"surface world, you decided to gain citizenship as a member of South Gate "
"Station. Amazingly, they actually accepted you."
msgstr "为了远离新英格兰地表世界的痛苦漩涡，你决定成为南门站的公民以寻求庇护。令人惊讶的是，他们竟然接纳了你。"

