msgid "South Gate Junker"
msgstr "南门站拾荒者"

#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "South Gate Junker"
msgstr "南门站拾荒者"

#. ~ Profession (male South Gate Junker) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were never content to just stay within the protective embrace of South "
"Gate. You saw other citizens as being too cowardly, too afraid, too soft. "
"You decided to buck their trend, traipsing throughout the underrail to make "
"a name for yourself."
msgstr "你从不满足于仅仅待在南门站的保护之下。你认为其他公民太过懦弱、恐惧和软弱。你决定逆流而行，在地下铁路各处游荡，为自己闯出一番名声。"

