#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "South Gate Computer Technician"
msgstr "南门站计算机技术员"

#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "South Gate Computer Technician"
msgstr "南门站计算机技术员"

#. ~ Profession (male South Gate Computer Technician) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Seeking refuge away from the maelstrom of pain that is the New England "
"surface world, you decided to gain citizenship as a member of South Gate "
"Station. Amazingly, they actually accepted you. After witnessing line upon "
"line of code in the various consoles of SGS, you began to see a rythm to the"
" apparently madness of programming. You became a well-respected member of "
"South Gate Station's IT department."
msgstr ""
"为了远离新英格兰地表世界的痛苦漩涡，你决定成为南门站的公民以寻求庇护。令人惊讶的是，他们竟然接纳了你。在目睹了SGS各种控制台上一行又一行的代码后，你开始从看似疯狂的编程中看到了某种节奏。你成为了南门站IT部门中备受尊敬的成员。"

#. ~ Profession (female South Gate Computer Technician) description
#: .\subway_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Seeking refuge away from the maelstrom of pain that is the New England "
"surface world, you decided to gain citizenship as a member of South Gate "
"Station. Amazingly, they actually accepted you. After witnessing line upon "
"line of code in the various consoles of SGS, you began to see a rythm to the"
" apparently madness of programming. You became a well-respected member of "
