#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_heavy_guard.json .\ticketcards\red_spawncard.json
#: .\ticketcards\reich_spawncard.json
msgid "Protects the station from assailants"
msgstr "保护车站免受袭击者侵害"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
msgid "Red Line Merchant"
msgstr "红线商人"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "I'm a merchant."
msgstr "我是一名商人。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "Do you have anything for me to buy?"
msgstr "你有什么东西可以卖给我吗？"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_redmerchant.json
msgid ""
"Resources are tight, but we have more stuff than the reich. That much I can "
"say with certainty."
msgstr "资源紧张，但我们的东西比帝国多。这一点我可以肯定地说。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichciv.json
msgid "Reich Civilian"
msgstr "帝国平民"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichciv.json
msgid "A typical citizen of the 4th Reich."
msgstr "一个典型的第四帝国公民。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichheavy.json
msgid "Reich Heavy Soldier"
msgstr "帝国重装士兵"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid "Reich Merchant"
msgstr "帝国商人"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichmerchant.json
msgid ""
"Resources are tight, but we're better equipped than the reds. That much I "
"can say with certainty."
msgstr "资源紧张，但我们的装备比红军好。这一点我可以肯定地说。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichoff.json
msgid "Reich Officer"
msgstr "帝国军官"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichoff.json
msgid "An officer of the 4th Reich."
msgstr "第四帝国的一名军官。"

#: .\Metro\NPCs\metro_reichsoldier.json .\ticketcards\reich_spawncard.json
msgid "Reich Soldier"
msgstr "帝国士兵"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "communist officer's hat"
msgid_plural "communist officer's hats"
msgstr[0] "共产主义军官帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "communist officer's hat"}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"The only hat for a man of the proletarian revolution. Shoot dissidents, "
"reich fascists, dissidents and fascist dissidents disguised as civilians, "
"and look great doing it!"
msgstr "无产阶级革命者的专属帽子。用它来射杀异见分子、帝国法西斯分子、伪装成平民的异见分子和法西斯异见分子，同时保持帅气风范！"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "communist officer's coat"
msgid_plural "communist officer's coats"
msgstr[0] "共产主义军官外套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "communist officer's coat"}
#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thick leather jacket.  Protects against the cold of the metro when the "
"warmth of the revolutionary spirit isn't enough."
msgstr "一件厚实的皮夹克。当革命精神的热忱不足以抵御地铁的严寒时，它能提供保护。"

#: .\Metro\metro_armor\metro_armor.json
msgid "Red Line combat vest"
msgid_plural "Red Line combat vest"
msgstr[0] "红线战斗背心"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str_sp': 'Red Line combat vest'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str_sp': '4th Reich combat vest'}.
