msgstr "5毫米标准弹的空弹壳。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '8.6mm Standard Round'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An 8.6mm cartridge commonly seen in usage with high-power firearms common in"
" the underrail."
msgstr "一种8.6毫米弹药，常见于地铁下层轨道普遍使用的高威力枪械。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm Standard Round, reloaded"
msgid_plural "8.6mm Standard Round, reloadeds"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米标准弹，复装"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm Standard Round, black powder"
msgid_plural "8.6mm Standard Round, black powders"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米标准弹，黑火药"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm Standard Round JHP"
msgid_plural "8.6mm Standard Round JHPs"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米标准弹JHP"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '8.6mm Standard Round JHP'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 8.6mm cartridge commonly seen in usage with high-power firearms common in "
"the underrail. This variant features jacketed hollow point bullet in-lieu of"
" a conventional bullet, increasing stopping power."
msgstr "一种8.6毫米弹药，常见于地铁下层轨道普遍使用的高威力枪械。此变种采用被甲空尖弹代替常规子弹，增加了停止力。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm W2C Round"
msgid_plural "8.6mm W2C Rounds"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米W2C弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '8.6mm W2C Round'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An 8.6mm cartridge commonly seen in usage with high-power firearms common in"
" the underrail. This variant features tungsten carbide bullet in-lieu of a "
"conventional bullet, increasing stopping power."
msgstr "一种8.6毫米弹药，常见于地下铁路中高威力火器的使用。此型号采用碳化钨弹头替代常规子弹，增强了制止力。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "8.6mm standard round casing"
msgid_plural "8.6mm standard round casings"
msgstr[0] "8.6毫米标准弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '8.6mm standard round casing'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "An empty casing from a 8.6mm standard round."
msgstr "一枚8.6毫米标准弹的空弹壳。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "empty acid vial"
msgid_plural "empty acid vials"
msgstr[0] "空酸液瓶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'empty acid vial'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_ammo.json
msgid "An empty vial from an acid pistol."
msgstr "来自酸液手枪的空瓶。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_items.json
msgid "South Gate Station credit chit"
msgid_plural "South Gate Station credit chits"
msgstr[0] "南门站信用芯片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'South Gate Station credit chit'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_items.json
msgid ""
"A small stamped circuit containing a pre-set amount of South Gate credits, "
"popular in the underrail and quite valuable."
msgstr "一种小型压印电路，内含预设数量的南门站信用点，在地下铁路中很受欢迎且价值不菲。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid "psi beetle"
msgid_plural "psi beetles"
msgstr[0] "灵能甲虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'psi beetle'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Azuridae are mutated and enlarged insects that resemble Rhinoceros beetles, "
"instead of horns though, they have massive brains that they use to power "
"their psionic abilities. Azuridae are so called due to the azure hue on "
"their carapace. Their psionic powers have granted them nicknames such as psi"
" beetle and psi bug by residents of the Underrail."
msgstr ""
"蓝甲虫是变异并放大的昆虫，形似犀牛甲虫，但它们没有角，而是拥有巨大的大脑，用以驱动其灵能能力。因其甲壳上的天蓝色调而得名。它们的灵能力量使地下铁路居民给它们起了诸如“灵能甲虫”和“灵能虫”的绰号。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid "underrail crawler"
msgid_plural "underrail crawlers"
msgstr[0] "地下铁路爬行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'underrail crawler'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Crawlers live in dark places, both ruins and caves and haunt the nightmares "
"of Underrail and metro denizens alike. They look like pony-sized black "
"scorpions. Beware if you find one, for the few moments of your life left to "
"you might be brief."
msgstr ""
"爬行者栖息在黑暗之处，无论是废墟还是洞穴，它们萦绕在地下铁路和地铁居民的噩梦中。它们看起来像小马大小的黑色蝎子。如果你发现一只，请小心，因为你剩下的生命可能很短暂。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid "nosalis"
msgid_plural "nosaliss"
msgstr[0] "诺萨利斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nosalis'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Nosalises are the standard enemy of the metro. They are fierce predators, "
"extremely territorial, and can easily overwhelm fortified positions in large"
" numbers. Common between all types however, is a bipedal and humanoid shape "
"with two arms and legs, arched spines, and large round heads that "
"prominently display big noses, gaping jaws, and huge teeth. Their nests are "
"seemingly everywhere in the metro, but the creatures are less frequently "
"seen on the surface."
msgstr ""
"诺萨利斯是地铁中的标准敌人。它们是凶猛的掠食者，极具领地意识，数量众多时能轻易压倒防御阵地。所有类型的共同特征是双足人形，拥有双臂双腿、拱起的脊柱，以及突出显示大鼻子、张开的下颚和巨大牙齿的大圆头。它们的巢穴似乎遍布地铁各处，但在地表较少见到这些生物。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid "glow wort"
msgstr "发光苔藓"

#. ~ Description for glow wort
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid ""
"A bio-lumiscent mushroom that emits a low level of light as part of its "
"biological process."
msgstr "一种生物发光蘑菇，作为其生物过程的一部分，会发出低水平的光。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid "SMASH!"
msgstr "砰！"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid "flaming barrel"
msgstr "燃烧桶"

#. ~ Description for flaming barrel
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid ""
"A perforated barrel filled with some kind of combusting fuel to give light "
"to people around it."
msgstr "一个穿孔的桶，装满某种燃烧燃料，为周围的人们提供光亮。"

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid "electric lamp"
msgstr "电灯"

#. ~ Description for electric lamp
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_terrain.json
msgid "A simple electric lamp that emits energy via an electric current."
msgstr "一个简单的电灯，通过电流释放能量。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"Can't you see that I'm busy? whatever you wan't make sure it's important."
msgstr "没看见我正忙着吗？不管你想要什么，确保它很重要。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"How do you perform the job of being a councilor for South Gate station??"
msgstr "你如何履行南门站议员的职责？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Do you have a task for me?"
msgstr "你有任务给我吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"South Gate Station is led primarily by councilors. We are a small number of "
"people that comprise the ruling council of South Gate Station. Without our "
"guidance, the administration, engineering, life support, trade and security "
"of the entire SGS complex would probably fall into disarray."
msgstr ""
"南门站主要由议员领导。我们是一小群人，组成了南门站的统治议会。没有我们的指导，整个南门站综合体的行政、工程、生命支持、贸易和安全可能会陷入混乱。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Deal with the infestation"
msgstr "处理虫害"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"I know you're a bit new to the Underrail, but an infestation has come to our"
" attention near South Gate Station, and I want you to deal with it."
msgstr "我知道你对地下铁路还不太熟悉，但我们注意到南门站附近出现了虫害，我希望你去处理它。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Get to it, you know how infestations can get if we don't act quickly."
msgstr "快去处理，你知道如果我们不迅速行动，虫害会变得多严重。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Hm, I guess I'll just get one of the guards to deal with them!"
msgstr "嗯，我想我还是让一个守卫去处理它们吧！"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"Remember, Psibugs can induce a state of fear in their targets, please be "
"careful."
msgstr "记住，灵能虫能在目标身上诱发恐惧状态，请小心。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Has the infestation been dealt with?"
msgstr "虫害处理好了吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Great work, you've done South Great Station a great service."
msgstr "干得好，你为南门站立了大功。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "I'm not entirely sure if you're telling the truth, but alright."
msgstr "我不完全确定你说的是真话，但好吧。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "So the infestation isn't being dealt with?"
msgstr "那么虫害还没有被处理吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Kill Underrail Bandits"
msgstr "消灭地下铁路强盗"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Kill Underrail Bandits'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"A group of bandits have taken up a position near South Gate Station, find "
"them and kill them for us."
msgstr "一伙强盗在南门车站附近占据了据点，找到他们并替我们干掉他们。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"I need your help again, some bandits have set up camp near our station, and "
"extoring local travellers for their property. We need you to deal with it."
msgstr "我又需要你的帮助了，一些强盗在我们的车站附近扎营，向当地旅客勒索财物。我们需要你去处理一下。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Be sure to kill those people as soon as possible."
msgstr "务必尽快干掉那些人。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"Laziness of your caliber is rare, perhaps you're no better than the scum out"
" on the Underrail."
msgstr "像你这种程度的懒惰可不多见，也许你跟地铁里的那些渣滓没什么两样。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Don't underestimate these people, they're more robust than you think."
msgstr "别小看这些人，他们比你想象的要强悍得多。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Are they dead yet?"
msgstr "他们死了吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid ""
"South Gate Station is made safer by your efforts. Here, take these items as "
"a reward"
msgstr "多亏了你的努力，南门车站变得更安全了。来，把这些东西当作奖励拿去吧。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "What good does this do us?"
msgstr "这对我们有什么好处？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_admin.json
msgid "Alright, at least you tried."
msgstr "好吧，至少你尝试过了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
msgid "What do you want, why are you speaking to me anyway, girl?"
msgstr "你想干嘛，小姑娘，你到底为什么要跟我说话？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
msgid "What do you want, why are you speaking to me anyway?"
msgstr "你想干嘛，你到底为什么要跟我说话？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
msgid ""
"What's it like being a ruthless bandit, do you get the kill people often?"
msgstr "当个冷酷无情的强盗是什么感觉，你经常杀人吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "See you later."
msgstr "回头见。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
msgid ""
"Killing people? Have you been watching too many video tapes or something? "
"The criminal life isn't easy, friend, most of us barely get by. Sure, "
"assaulting random people for their stuff can be fun, but we're more than "
"just that."
msgstr ""
"杀人？你是不是录像带看多了还是怎么的？犯罪生活可不容易，朋友，我们大多数人勉强糊口而已。当然，随机袭击路人抢东西可能挺有趣，但我们不止干这个。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_bandit.json
msgid "I see."
msgstr "我明白了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json
msgid "What's it like living as member of South Gate Station?"
msgstr "作为南门车站的一员生活是怎样的？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_civ.json
msgid ""
"What is there to say really? It's far better than getting mauled to death by"
" whatever exists outside or on the surface world. Food is somewhat "
"plentiful, and things are clean."
msgstr "这有什么好说的呢？总比在外面或地表世界被什么东西撕成碎片强多了。食物还算充足，环境也干净。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json
msgid "How do you serve as a soldier for South Gate Station?"
msgstr "你是如何为南门车站当兵的？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_guardnpc.json
msgid ""
"It can be difficult at times, but it's better than being some pipe-worker "
"who gets stabbed by a nightstalker out of nowhere.."
msgstr "有时可能挺难的，但总比当个管道工，莫名其妙被夜行者捅死强。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid "Heya, Missy what's a girl like you doing around here? *burps*"
msgstr "嘿，小姐，像你这样的姑娘在这儿干嘛呢？*打嗝*"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid "Howdy partner, what are you doing moseying?"
msgstr "你好啊伙计，你在这儿溜达什么呢？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid "What's your deal anyway, buddy?"
msgstr "你到底想干嘛，老兄？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json .\ticketcards\red_talk_spawncard.json
#: .\ticketcards\reich_talk_spawncard.json
msgid "Want to travel with me?"
msgstr "想跟我一起旅行吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid ""
"MY deal? What's YOUR deal? You walk up to me and start asking inane "
"questions to every person you meet and you think we're always going to be "
"kind to you? How about some manners you cave hopper-brained imbecile."
msgstr "我想干嘛？你想干嘛？你走过来，见人就问些无聊的问题，还以为我们总会对你客客气气？懂点礼貌行吗，你这个洞穴跳鼠脑子的白痴。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\Talk_sgs_pipe.json
msgid "Okay, jeez."
msgstr "好吧，天哪。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_administrator.json
msgid "South Gate Councilor"
msgstr "南门车站议员"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_administrator.json
msgid "A councilor of South gate station."
msgstr "南门车站的一位议员。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_bandit.json
msgid "Underrail bandit"
msgstr "地铁强盗"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_bandit.json
msgid "Assaults denizens of the underrail and nabs their loot."
msgstr "袭击地铁居民并抢夺他们的战利品。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_civilian.json
msgid "South Gate Civilian"
msgstr "南门平民"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_civilian.json
msgid "A typical citizen of South Gate Station."
msgstr "南门车站的一位典型居民。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "South Gate Cook"
msgstr "南门车站厨师"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "I'm a local shopkeeper."
msgstr "我是本地店主。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "What is it like being a cook in this station?"
msgstr "在这个站点当厨师感觉如何？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Could I get any food?"
msgstr "我能弄点吃的吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"I truly love my job around here. Sure the food might be pretty basic: a few "
"selections of cavehopper meat and farmed potatoes, but it never gets old "
"seeing the look on people's faces when they eat this slop."
msgstr "我真的很喜欢我在这儿的工作。当然，食物可能很简单：几种洞穴跳鼠肉和种植的土豆，但看到人们吃这玩意儿时的表情，这种感觉永远不会过时。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve a copy of Cooking on a
#. Budget.'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Retrieve a copy of Cooking on a Budget."
msgstr "取回一本《预算烹饪》的副本。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"I'll let you in on a little secret, well perhaps it's not very little. I'm "
"not a very good cook and I think people are starting to become aware of "
"that, could you help me out by finding me a cookbook, it would be a great "
"help."
msgstr "我告诉你一个小秘密，嗯，也许这秘密不算小。我厨艺不精，而且我觉得大家开始察觉到了，你能帮我找本烹饪书吗？那会帮上大忙的。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Help me find a copy of the book 'Cooking on a Budget'. I'm not a very good "
"cook, and I could use the knowledge contained within that text."
msgstr "帮我找一本《预算烹饪》的书。我厨艺不太好，那本书里的知识应该能派上用场。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer."
msgstr "感谢你接受我的提议。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Ouch, I guess people are gonna have to get used to cave hopper burgers for a"
" long while."
msgstr "哎哟，看来大家得习惯洞穴跳鼠汉堡很长一段时间了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Libraries, Schools and Homes might have a cookbook or two, see what you can "
"find."
msgstr "图书馆、学校和住宅里可能有一两本烹饪书，看看你能找到什么。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Have you found what I requested yet?"
msgstr "你找到我要的东西了吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Great work, I'll become a master chef in no time."
msgstr "干得好，我很快就能成为大厨了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "That's odd, I don't really know what to say."
msgstr "真奇怪，我都不知道该说什么了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. It's just that food will be as bland as ever."
msgstr "好吧，你尽力了。只是食物还是会像以前一样寡淡无味。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "South Gate Doctor"
msgstr "南门医生"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "What is it like being a doctor in this station?"
msgstr "在这个站点当医生感觉如何？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"It's actually pretty easy, all things considered. Most of the time people "
"come back with little more than a few cave hopper scratches. Watch out for "
"nighstalkers though, they can be pretty nasty."
msgstr "说实话，考虑到所有情况，这其实挺简单的。大多数时候人们回来时都只带着几道洞穴跳鼠的抓痕。不过要小心夜行者，它们可能相当棘手。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve a syringe of adrenaline.'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Retrieve a syringe of adrenaline."
msgstr "取回一支肾上腺素注射器。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Look, I'm a bit busy here, but I think you could help me out here. I fear "
"that more skirmishes with other stations are on the horizon, and its "
"imperative that we prepare for any eventuality. Would you be willing to get "
"me an adrenaline syringe?"
msgstr ""
"听着，我这儿有点忙，但我觉得你能帮上忙。我担心与其他站点的冲突即将爆发，我们必须为任何可能发生的情况做好准备。你愿意帮我弄一支肾上腺素注射器吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Would you be willing to get me an adrenaline syringe? I think the troops out"
" in the Underrail would greatly appreciate it."
msgstr "你愿意帮我弄一支肾上腺素注射器吗？我想地下铁路的士兵们会非常感激的。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "That's unfortunate."
msgstr "真遗憾。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Look for doctor's officers and hospitals on the surface, you'll probably "
"find some there."
msgstr "去地面的医生办公室和医院找找，那里可能有一些。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Great work, this adrenaline will be useful."
msgstr "干得好，这肾上腺素会很有用的。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. but it's unfortunate that we'll be lacking "
"adrenaline."
msgstr "好吧，你已经尽力了。但遗憾的是，我们将缺少肾上腺素了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_guard.json
msgid "South Gate Guard"
msgstr "南门站守卫"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "South Gate Gun Merchant"
msgstr "南门枪械商人"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "South Gate Gun merchant"
msgstr "南门枪械商人"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "What are you buying, what are you selling?"
msgstr "你想买什么，卖什么？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "What is it like being a gun merchant around here?"
msgstr "在这附近当枪械商人感觉如何？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Would you be willing to let me buy anything?"
msgstr "你愿意让我买点东西吗？"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"You would be surprised at the amount of business we get, even all the way "
"down here in a subway. I guess it pays to be a safe-haven in an unsafe "
"world. A lot of people are pretty confused by our guns though, it's like "
"they've never seen them before."
msgstr ""
"你会惊讶于我们这里的生意有多好，即使是在地铁这么深的地方。我想，在一个不安全的世界里，成为一个安全港是值得的。不过很多人对我们的枪感到困惑，就好像他们以前从未见过似的。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Retrieve two firearm repair kits"
msgstr "取回两个枪械维修工具包"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve two firearm repair kits'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Retrieve two firearm repair kits for the Gun Merchant."
msgstr "为枪械商人取回两个枪械维修工具包。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I've been running low on gun repair kits. It seems like conflict with other "
"stations has flared up again recently, and we're quickly running through "
"supplies. We'll reach a maintenance bottleneck soon, and we can't afford to "
"have that happen."
msgstr "我的枪械维修工具包快用完了。最近似乎与其他站点的冲突又激化了，我们的物资消耗得很快。很快我们就会面临维护瓶颈，我们可承担不起这种情况。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I would appreciate it greatly if you could get me two firearm repair kits, "
"if that's not too much to ask."
msgstr "如果你能给我弄两个枪械维修工具包，我将不胜感激，如果这要求不算太过分的话。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I thank you for accepting this, now make it quick, we don't have time to "
"spare."
msgstr "感谢你接受这个任务，现在动作快点，我们没有多余的时间了。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"That's unfortunate, but I guess I'll have to find some way to make things "
"work out."
msgstr "那真遗憾，但我想我得想办法解决这个问题。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Gun stores on the surface probably have firearm repair kits, perhaps you "
"could even make one yourself if you know enough."
msgstr "地面的枪店可能有枪械维修工具包，如果你懂得足够多，或许甚至可以自己做一个。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Great work, things in South Gate just got a little safer thanks to you."
msgstr "干得好，多亏了你，南门的情况稍微安全了一些。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. It's just that things will get more difficult "
"fron now on."
msgstr "好吧，你已经尽力了。只是从现在开始，事情会变得更困难。"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_heavy_guard.json
msgid "South Gate Heavy Guard"
msgstr "南门重装守卫"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_pipeworker.json
msgid "Pipeworker"
msgstr "管道工"

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_pipeworker.json
msgid "A pipeworker."
msgstr "一名管道工。"

#: .\UnderRail\SGS_maps\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "South Gate Outpost"
msgstr "南门前哨站"

#: .\UnderRail\SGS_maps\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "Underrail Cave"
msgstr "地下铁路洞穴"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "South Gate Station Security Uniform"
msgid_plural "South Gate Station Security Uniform"
msgstr[0] "南门站安保制服"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'South Gate Station Security Uniform'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid ""
"The standard and uniformly dull blue uniform worn by most members of the "
"South Gate Station security detail. Often associated with bravery, or a "
"quick death."
msgstr "南门站安保人员普遍穿着的标准且单调的蓝色制服。常与英勇或快速死亡联系在一起。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "Cave Hopper Leather Armor"
msgid_plural "Cave Hopper Leather Armor"
msgstr[0] "洞穴跳跃者皮甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Cave Hopper Leather Armor'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid ""
"A rather lightweight armor protecting user's vital torso area, in addition "
"to some arm protection. This armor is made of cave hopper leather. ."
msgstr "一种相当轻便的护甲，保护使用者躯干要害区域，并提供部分手臂防护。此护甲由洞穴跳跃者皮革制成。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "South Gate Station security vest"
msgid_plural "South Gate Station security vest"
msgstr[0] "南门站安保背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'South Gate Station security vest'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid ""
"A nylon vest equipped with several pouches for magazine and ammunition "
"storage. Comes pre-equipped with several light ballistic plates that provide"
" a small modicum of protection."
msgstr "一件尼龙背心，配备多个用于存放弹匣和弹药的袋子。预装数块轻型防弹板，提供少量防护。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "Underrail Metal Armor"
msgid_plural "Underrail Metal Armors"
msgstr[0] "地下铁路金属护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Underrail Metal Armor'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid ""
"Near all-encompasing suit of metal armor. Outfitted with enough steel plates"
" to cover the overwhelming majority of the user's body. Its immense "
"protection comes with a drawback: its immense weight and incumberence for "
"all but strong users."
msgstr "几乎覆盖全身的金属护甲。配备足够钢板以覆盖使用者绝大部分身体。其强大的防护力伴随缺点：极重，除强壮者外均感笨重。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid "Underrail metal helmet"
msgid_plural "Underrail metal helmets"
msgstr[0] "地下铁路金属头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Underrail metal helmet'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_armor\sgs_armor.json
msgid ""
"A helmet made from plates of steel with a visor of ballistic glass. Made for"
" use in tandem with underrail metal armor."
msgstr "由钢板制成、配有防弹玻璃面罩的头盔。设计用于与地下铁路金属护甲搭配使用。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_crossbows.json
msgid "Zephyr crossbow"
msgid_plural "Zephyr crossbows"
msgstr[0] "西风弩"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_crossbows.json
msgid ""
"A light crossbow common amongst the more poor denizens of the underrail.  "
"Stronger people can reload it much faster.  Bolts fired from this weapon "
"have a good chance of remaining intact for re-use. Why one would use these "
"instead of firearms is unknown, but many swear by them."
msgstr ""
"地下铁路较贫困居民中常见的轻型弩。强壮者能更快装填。此武器发射的弩箭有很大几率保持完好以供重复使用。为何有人选择它而非枪械原因不明，但许多人对其深信不疑。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_crossbows.json
msgid "Cyclon crossbow"
msgid_plural "Cyclon crossbows"
msgstr[0] "旋风弩"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_crossbows.json
msgid ""
"A high-power crossbow with with an intricate 4-bar mechanism to reduce felt "
"load when tensing the crossbow.  Takes less time to reload due to a modern "
"string-pulling system, but comes at the expense of stopping power."
msgstr "一种高威力弩，采用精密的四杆机构以减少张弩时的负荷感。因现代拉弦系统装填时间更短，但以停止力为代价。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_melee.json
msgid "shock steel sledge hammer"
msgid_plural "shock steel sledge hammers"
msgstr[0] "电击钢制大锤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shock steel sledge hammer'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_melee.json
msgid ""
"A large, heavy hammer.  Makes an acceptable melee weapon for the very "
"strong, but is nearly useless in the hands of the weak. This variant has "
"been outfitted with electrodes, making it useful to shock people with."
msgstr "一把沉重的大锤。对极强者而言是合格的近战武器，但在弱者手中几乎无用。此版本配备电极，可用于电击目标。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_melee.json
msgid "shock dagger"
msgid_plural "shock daggerss"
msgstr[0] "电击匕首"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shock dagger', 'str_pl': 'shock daggerss'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_melee.json
msgid ""
"This is a combat knife common to the underrail.  It is light and extremely "
"sharp, and could be deadly in either the right hands or when attached as a "
"bayonet. This version has been outfitted with electrodes, allowing the user "
"to shock their target before going in for a stab."
msgstr "这是地下铁路常见的战斗刀。轻便且极其锋利，在合适者手中或作为刺刀时可致命。此版本配备电极，允许使用者在刺击前电击目标。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid "Hawker extended magazine"
msgid_plural "Hawker extended magazines"
msgstr[0] "霍克扩展弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hawker extended magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid ""
"An extended 28-round polymer magazine for use with standard round compatible"
" firearms."
msgstr "一种28发聚合物扩展弹匣，适用于兼容标准弹药的枪械。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid "Hawker magazine"
msgid_plural "Hawker magazines"
msgstr[0] "霍克弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hawker magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid ""
"A compact light-weight polymer magazine for use with 5mm standard round "
"compatible firearms."
msgstr "一种紧凑轻量聚合物弹匣，适用于兼容5毫米标准弹药的枪械。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid "Hawker pistol"
msgid_plural "Hawker pistols"
msgstr[0] "霍克手枪"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid ""
"A weak pistol common amongst all strata of the underrail, from the lowest "
"junkyard mutant to the highest protectorate officer. Prized by all for its "
"ease of use, low production costs, and relatively common ammunition."
msgstr "一种弱效手枪，在地下铁路各阶层中普遍使用，从最低等的垃圾场变种人到最高级的保护国军官。因其易用性、低生产成本和相对常见的弹药而备受珍视。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid "South Gate laser pistol"
msgid_plural "South Gate laser pistols"
msgstr[0] "南门激光手枪"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid ""
"This model of laser pistol is one of a rare type in the underail. Most "
"denizens of the underrail are more than content to meet their death at the "
"hands of a firearm, but few are ready for a laser weapon!"
msgstr "这款激光手枪是地下铁路中罕见的类型。大多数居民满足于死于枪械，但很少有人准备好面对激光武器！"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid "Acid Pistol"
msgid_plural "Acid Pistols"
msgstr[0] "酸液手枪"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgid ""
"A curious and rare pistol in the underrail. What's not so curious is what "
"its acid vials do to your skin when they want to dissolve it into its base "
"components."
msgstr "地下铁路中一种奇特而罕见的手枪。其酸液瓶欲将皮肤溶解成基本成分时的效果并不令人好奇。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_pistols.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "pistol"
msgstr "手枪"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "Hornet 30-round magazine"
msgid_plural "Hornet 30-round magazines"
msgstr[0] "黄蜂30发弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hornet 30-round magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A standard capacity 30-round box magazine for use with the Hornet 7.62mm "
"assault rifles."
msgstr "标准容量30发盒式弹匣，适用于黄蜂7.62毫米突击步枪。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "Marauder 25-round magazine"
msgid_plural "Marauder 25-round magazines"
msgstr[0] "掠夺者25发弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Marauder 25-round magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A standard capacity 25-round box magazine for use with Marauder 8.6mm "
"compatible rifles."
msgstr "一种标准容量的25发盒式弹匣，适用于兼容掠夺者8.6毫米口径的步枪。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "spearhead magazine"
msgid_plural "spearhead magazines"
msgstr[0] "矛头弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spearhead magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A stadard 10-round steel box magazine compatible with 7.62 Spearhead rifle."
msgstr "一种标准的10发钢制盒式弹匣，兼容7.62毫米矛头步枪。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "Hornet 7.62mm"
msgid_plural "Hornet 7.62mms"
msgstr[0] "黄蜂7.62毫米"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"The Hornet is a protectorate assault rifle that uses a bullpup design.  It "
"is often seen as the long arm of the protectorate, although is also popular "
"with other civilized stations, such as South Gate."
msgstr "黄蜂是一种采用无托设计的保护国突击步枪。它常被视为保护国的长臂武器，但也深受其他文明站点如南门的欢迎。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "Marauder 8.6mm"
msgid_plural "Marauder 8.6mms"
msgstr[0] "掠夺者8.6毫米"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"The Marauder is a core-city assault rifle that uses a bullpup design.  It is"
" often seen in use among the private security groups that essentially serve "
"as private armies."
msgstr "掠夺者是一种采用无托设计的核心城市突击步枪。它常见于私人安保团体中，这些团体实质上充当着私人军队的角色。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "3 rd."
msgstr "3 发"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid "7.62mm Spearhead"
msgid_plural "7.62mm Spearhead"
msgstr[0] "7.62毫米矛头"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_rifles.json
msgid ""
"A famed 7.62mm Spearhead sniper rifle. Purported to once be far, far more "
"powerful than it now is."
msgstr "一把著名的7.62毫米矛头狙击步枪。据称其威力曾远超现在。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "Jackrabbit magazine"
msgid_plural "Jackrabbit magazines"
msgstr[0] "杰克兔弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Jackrabbit magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid ""
"A standard 30-round steel box magazine for use with the Jackrabbit SMG."
msgstr "一种标准的30发钢制盒式弹匣，适用于杰克兔冲锋枪。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "Steel Cat extended magazine"
msgid_plural "Steel Cat extended magazines"
msgstr[0] "钢猫扩容弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Steel Cat extended magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid ""
"A drum magazine for use with the Steel Cat SMG.  Much greater capacity but "
"less reliable the factory specification magazine."
msgstr "一种适用于钢猫冲锋枪的弹鼓。容量更大，但可靠性低于工厂规格弹匣。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "Steel Cat magazine"
msgid_plural "Steel Cat magazines"
msgstr[0] "钢猫弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Steel Cat magazine'}
#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "A standard capacity curved magazine for use with the Steel Cat SMG."
msgstr "一种标准容量的弧形弹匣，适用于钢猫冲锋枪。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "Jackrabbit 5mm"
msgid_plural "Jackrabbit 5mm"
msgstr[0] "杰克兔5毫米"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid ""
"The jacrabbit is well deserving of its namesake. As far as SMGs go, its very"
" rapid, albeit uncontrollable for inexperienced users."
msgstr "杰克兔名副其实。就冲锋枪而言，它射速极快，但对于经验不足的使用者来说难以控制。"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid "Steel Cat 8.6mm"
msgid_plural "Steel Cat 8.6mms"
msgstr[0] "钢猫8.6毫米"

#: .\UnderRail\underrail_weapons\sgs_smg.json
msgid ""
"The Steel Cat is one of the most widely-used submachine guns in the entire "
"underrail, and has been adopted by special forces and general security "
"alike."
msgstr "钢猫是整个地下铁路中使用最广泛的冲锋枪之一，已被特种部队和普通安保人员广泛采用。"

#: .\ticketcards\red_talk_spawncard.json
msgid "Hello comrade officer, I am ready to join you on your journey!"
msgstr "你好，同志军官，我已准备好加入你的旅程！"

