#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\red_factionchange.json
#: Change\reich_factionchange.json Change\sgs_factionchange.json
msgid "Faction Changer"
msgstr "派系转换器"

#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\red_factionchange.json
#: Change\reich_factionchange.json Change\sgs_factionchange.json
msgid ""
"A stopgap to allow the user to change their faction at the start of the "
"game."
msgstr "一种权宜之计，允许使用者在游戏开始时更改其所属派系。"

#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\red_factionchange.json
msgid "Red Line faction change device"
msgid_plural "Red Line faction change devices"
msgstr[0] "红线派系转换装置"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Red Line faction change device'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': '4th Reich faction change device'}
#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\red_factionchange.json
#: Change\reich_factionchange.json
msgid ""
"A device used to decrease the player character's relationship with the 4th "
"Reich and South Gate Station. Should only be available at spawn, otherwise a"
" glitch has occurred."
msgstr "一种用于降低玩家角色与第四帝国及南门站关系的装置。应仅在生成时可用，否则为程序错误。"

#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\reich_factionchange.json
msgid "4th Reich faction change device"
msgid_plural "4th Reich faction change devices"
msgstr[0] "第四帝国派系变更装置"

#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\sgs_factionchange.json
msgid "South Gate faction change device"
msgid_plural "South Gate faction change devices"
msgstr[0] "南门派系变更装置"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'South Gate faction change device'}
#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\sgs_factionchange.json
msgid ""
"A device used to decrease the player character's relationship with the 4th "
"Reich and Red Line. Should only be available at spawn, otherwise a glitch "
"has occurred."
msgstr "一种用于降低玩家角色与第四帝国及红线关系的装置。应仅在生成时可用，否则为程序错误。"

#: .\ticketcards\Faction Change\talk_red_factioncharge.json
#: Change\talk_reich_factioncharge.json
msgid ""
"Hello lady, I am a stopgap to allow the user to change their faction at the "
"start of the game. Otherwise it would be impossible to play for the Red Line"
" Profession Start."
msgstr "你好女士，我是一个临时方案，允许用户在游戏开始时变更派系。否则无法进行红线职业开局。"

